window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When one of the world’s most horrific assassins unleashes a worldwide campaign of terror, American covert operative, Chase Fulton, and his team of elite warriors must stop him before the carnage falls too close to home.<br> <br> Tactical Team 21’s fingerprints are intricately woven throughout a stream of international horrors as the killer devours his way across Europe before unleashing his personal Armageddon on the American Homeland. If the team can’t find him and drive a sword through soulless chest, everything they hold dear will be ripped from beneath them, leaving them dangling above a hell of their own creation.<br> <br> Feel the tension and taste the adrenalin as Chase and the team must stand toe to toe with a raging evil that seems to feed on their every move.<br> <br> Never before has there been so much to lose. Never before have the fires of battle burned so hot beneath their feet. Never before has victory felt more like ultimate defeat.</p>"; 
